The '''23rd Bangladesh National Film Awards''', presented by Ministry of Information, Bangladesh to felicitate the best of Bangladeshi Cinema released in the year 1998. The ceremony took place in Dhaka and awards were given by then President of Bangladesh. The National Film Awards are the only film awards given by the government itself. Every year, a national panel appointed by the government selects the winning entry, and the award ceremony is held in [[Dhaka]]. 1998 was the 23rd ceremony of [[National Film Awards (Bangladesh)|National Film Awards]].<ref name=bdnews24>{{cite news |author=Rashed Shaon |date= |script-title=চার দশকে আমাদের সেরা চলচ্চিত্রগুলো |trans-title=The Best Films in Four Decades |url=http://glitz.bdnews24.com/details.php?catry=2&showns=2012 |language=bn |work=bdnews24.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127231625/http://glitz.bdnews24.com/details.php?catry=2&showns=2012 |archivedate=January 27, 2013 |accessdate=November 4, 2012}}</ref>
